A method that interacts with multiple tables could be:
```sql
method get_total_order_value(order_id = int) = decimal;
begin
    declare total_amount decimal;
    select sum(p.Price * o.Quantity) into total_amount from Orders o join OrderItems oi on o.OrderID = oi.OrderID join Products p on oi.ProductID = p.ProductID where o.OrderID = order_id;
    return total_amount;
end;
```

